---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title='SideUp — Landing Page'>
<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Side<span>Up</span></div>
  <a class="nav-cta" href="https://t.me/sideupbot">Open @sideupbot</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="live-badge">
    <span class="live-dot"></span>
    Live now on Telegram
  </div>
  <h1>Your friend<br>talks big.<br><em>Make them prove it.</em></h1>
  <p>SideUp locks your sports challenge in escrow inside Telegram — winner gets paid automatically when the match ends. Zero flaking. Zero house edge.</p>
  <div class="hero-buttons">
    <a class="btn-primary" href="https://t.me/sideupbot">⚡ Open @sideupbot</a>
    <a class="btn-secondary" href="#how-it-works">See how it works</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Bot preview card -->
  <div class="bot-preview">
    <div class="bot-header">
      <div class="bot-avatar">S</div>
      <div>
        <div class="bot-name">SideUp</div>
        <div class="bot-handle">@sideupbot</div>
      </div>
      <div class="online-dot"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="chat-messages">
      <div class="msg">
        <div class="msg-match">⚽ Arsenal vs Man City</div>
        <div class="msg-sub">Premier League · Sat 15:00</div>
        <div>Pick your side:</div>
        <div class="side-btns" style="margin-top:8px">
          <div class="side-btn green">🔴 Arsenal</div>
          <div class="side-btn">Draw</div>
          <div class="side-btn">🔵 Man City</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="msg" style="font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--text-muted)">
        Arsenal, <strong style="color:var(--text)">⭐ 500 Stars</strong>
        <div class="link-preview">Share: t.me/sideupbot?start=ref_8f2a</div>
      </div>
      <div class="msg msg-locked">🔒 Stakes locked in escrow. Match starts in 12 min.</div>
      <div class="msg msg-win">🏆 You won! ⭐ 980 Stars sent to your account.<br><span style="font-size:0.78rem;opacity:0.8">FT: Arsenal 2–1 Man City</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">0%</div><div class="stat-label">commission at launch</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">P2P</div><div class="stat-label">no house, pure escrow</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">Auto</div><div class="stat-label">result verification</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">Inside Telegram</div><div class="stat-label">no app download needed</div></div>
</div>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how-it-works">
  <span class="section-tag">How it works</span>
  <h2>Three steps.<br>No friction.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Challenge creation to automatic payout — all inside Telegram.</p>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <h3>Pick your side</h3>
      <p>Open @sideupbot, choose a live match — Premier League, NBA, Champions League — and pick Home, Draw, or Away.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <h3>Lock stakes in escrow</h3>
      <p>Set your amount in Telegram Stars. Share your invite link. Your friend accepts the opposite side — both stakes are locked. No one can back out.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <h3>Winner gets paid</h3>
      <p>The moment the final whistle blows, SideUp confirms the result via live sports data and sends the full pot to the winner automatically. No disputes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SPORTS CALENDAR -->
<section>
  <span class="section-tag">Supported sports</span>
  <h2>Big matches.<br>Bigger bragging rights.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Live challenges across the world's most-argued-about sports — with more leagues added every week.</p>
  <div class="sports-grid">
    <div class="sport-card">
      <div class="sport-emoji">⚽</div>
      <div>
        <div class="sport-name">Football</div>
        <div class="sport-leagues">Premier League · Champions League · World Cup · Serie A · Bundesliga</div>
        <span class="sport-badge">LIVE</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sport-card">
      <div class="sport-emoji">🏀</div>
      <div>
        <div class="sport-name">Basketball</div>
        <div class="sport-leagues">NBA · NBA Finals · EuroLeague · FIBA World Cup</div>
        <span class="sport-badge">LIVE</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sport-card">
      <div class="sport-emoji">🏆</div>
      <div>
        <div class="sport-name">More coming</div>
        <div class="sport-leagues">Tennis · Ice Hockey · MMA · Cricket · F1 — vote for your league below</div>
        <span class="sport-badge soon">SOON</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Upcoming events -->
  <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--text-muted); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:16px; font-weight:700;">🔥 Hot upcoming challenges</p>
    <div class="events-grid">
      <div class="event-card featured">
        <div class="event-label">⚽ Football</div>
        <div class="event-name">Champions League Final</div>
        <div class="event-date">May 30, 2025 · 20:00 CET</div>
        <a class="event-cta" href="https://t.me/sideupbot">Challenge now →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="event-card">
        <div class="event-label">🏀 Basketball</div>
        <div class="event-name">NBA Finals Game 1</div>
        <div class="event-date">June 2025 · TBD</div>
        <a class="event-cta" href="https://t.me/sideupbot">Challenge now →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="event-card">
        <div class="event-label">🏆 Football</div>
        <div class="event-name">FIFA World Cup 2026</div>
        <div class="event-date">Summer 2026 · Be ready</div>
        <span style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size:0.85rem;">Coming soon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ESCROW EXPLAINER -->
<section>
  <div class="escrow-section">
    <span class="section-tag">Why it works</span>
    <h2>No house edge.<br>No bookmaker.<br>Just escrow.</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); max-width:580px; margin-top:12px;">SideUp is a technology platform, not a gambling operator. We hold your stakes — like PayPal holds a payment — and release them automatically when a public sports result is confirmed. We don't set odds. We don't take a position. We don't profit if you lose.</p>
    <p style="color:var(--text-muted); max-width:580px; margin-top:12px;">Think of it as Venmo for friend challenges: two people, equal stakes, automatic settlement. The result comes from a neutral third-party sports API — not us.</p>
    <div class="escrow-points">
      <div class="escrow-point">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:8px;">🔒</div>
        <h3>Funds locked at accept</h3>
        <p>Both parties lock stakes before the match starts. Nobody can back out once the game is live.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="escrow-point">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:8px;">⚡</div>
        <h3>Instant auto-payout</h3>
        <p>Results are pulled from live football-data.org and balldontlie.io APIs. No manual review. No delays. No disputes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="escrow-point">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:8px;">⭐</div>
        <h3>Telegram Stars only</h3>
        <p>No credit cards. No crypto wallets. No KYC friction. SideUp uses Telegram's native payment layer — already on your phone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="escrow-point">
        <div style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:8px;">👥</div>
        <h3>Two modes: private or open</h3>
        <p>Challenge a specific friend with a private link, or post to The Market — an open list where anyone can accept.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section>
  <span class="section-tag">FAQ</span>
  <h2>Real questions.<br>Straight answers.</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">The stuff you're actually wondering about.</p>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <details>
      <summary>Is this gambling? Am I breaking the law?</summary>
      <div class="faq-body"><strong>No.</strong> SideUp is an escrow technology platform — not a gambling operator. We don't set odds, take positions, or profit from your losses. Two individuals agree to a challenge, lock equal funds, and the winner is determined by a publicly verifiable sports result. SideUp is the technical intermediary, like PayPal processing a payment between friends. You are responsible for compliance with your local laws. SideUp does not operate as a gambling service in any jurisdiction.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>What are Telegram Stars?</summary>
      <div class="faq-body">Telegram Stars (XTR) is Telegram's native in-app currency — you can buy them with a regular credit or debit card inside the Telegram app. No crypto wallet, no sign-up beyond Telegram. Think of them like app store credits. When you win, Stars are sent directly to your Telegram account.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>What happens if the match is cancelled or postponed?</summary>
      <div class="faq-body">If a match is officially postponed or cancelled, both stakes are returned in full to each participant. No fee. No fuss. The escrow only releases when a confirmed final result exists.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Does SideUp take a cut?</summary>
      <div class="faq-body">At launch: <strong>0% commission</strong>. Every challenge is completely free. Once we scale, challenges above a threshold will carry a small 2% platform fee — still less than anything you'd pay anywhere else. Free challenges remain free forever for small amounts.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Can I challenge a stranger?</summary>
      <div class="faq-body">Yes — via The Market. Post your open challenge and anyone in the SideUp community can accept the opposite side. Great for when your friends won't pick the wrong team.</div>
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Do I need to download anything?</summary>
      <div class="faq-body">No. SideUp is a Telegram bot. If you have Telegram (and you do), you're ready. Just open @sideupbot and start challenging.</div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA SECTION -->
<div class="cta-section">
  <h2>No house.<br>Just you<br>and them.</h2>
  <p>Stop letting your friends dodge the payout. Challenge them on Telegram right now — it's free, it's instant, and the bot doesn't forget.</p>
  <a class="btn-primary" href="https://t.me/sideupbot" style="display:inline-flex; font-size:1.1rem; padding:18px 40px;">
    ⚡ Open @sideupbot on Telegram
  </a>
  <p class="cta-sub">Free to start. No download. No credit card.</p>
</div>

<!-- EMAIL CAPTURE -->
<div class="email-section">
  <h3>Get the launch alert</h3>
  <p>We'll tell you when your favourite league goes live.</p>
  <div class="email-form">
    <input class="email-input" type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" />
    <button class="email-btn">Notify me</button>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
</Base>
